note bottom of CollisionScenario
  stepOnce() calls:
  1. pipeline_->detectCollisions()
  2. pipeline_->createConstraints()
  3. pipeline_->assembleSolverInput()
  4. lastResult_ = pipeline_->solveConstraintsWithWarmStart(dt)
  5. pipeline_->applyForces() [if applyForces=true]
  6. pipeline_->correctPositions() [if correctPositions=true]
  Returns lastResult_ by value; getLastSolveResult() returns const ref.

  Owned via unique_ptr<CollisionPipeline> because CollisionPipeline
  deletes all copy and move — unique_ptr makes CollisionScenario movable.
end note

